Requirements:
* e2fslib 
   Gentoo: emerge sys-fs/e2fsprogs
   Ubuntu: apt-get install e2fslibs-dev
* nasm
* g++
* bochs
  Gentoo: USE="X -debugger" emerge app-emulation/bochs
  Ubuntu: apt-get install bochs-x
  (change bochsrc as appropriate)
* Mercurial (aka: "hg") 
* Basic Shell Commands like: test, wc, grep, awk, make, md5sum, ...
